data.description: NEW ROOF RECENTLY INSTALLED!  Very nice 2 bedroom/2 bath home located on a quiet street in the gated Copper Crest community. Large living room and extra room that can be used as a dining room or family room. Breakfast nook off kitchen has great mountain views. Kitchen has ample cabinets and counter space. AZ room off family room can be used however a Buyer wishes. Covered patio in the front along with a covered sitting area behind AZ room. Very large storage/workshop is located behind carport. Copper Crest is an Active Adult Community which includes swimming, spa, shuffleboard, pool table, work-out facility, hiking and biking, and more. And, all within a short distance of Tucson.  And you own the land!
